abstract: Stock markets rise after Federal Reserve decides to keep interest rates unchanged for present.
lead_paragraph: A modest rebound in China also helped lift the Dow, the S.&P. 500 and the Nasdaq.

headline.main: With Fed Content to Wait, Investors Push Markets Higher
